{"tid":1458362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣內容要易入口","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:31.000Z","uid":273948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f8a3a9a8767452696a27902caf7ac79f90e2fe","tid":1458362,"uid":273948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:31.000Z","msg":"利申:學術研究<br />\n由6月至今見過唔少文宣 包括黃同藍色<br />\n係咪已經歸咗邊就冇得轉?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眼見2個月嚟有唔少人會變黃 特別喺噚晚之後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以文宣工作唔可以停 而且要變下形式!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我媽媽經歷過文化大革命，有少少野想同大家講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456583</a><br />\n<br />\n裡面有值得學嘅地方 e.g. <span style=\"color: red;\">煽情 偷換概念</span><br />\n同埋要<span style=\"color: red;\">塑造示威者形象</span> 咁先打到人情牌<br />\n你見警方/政府新聞稿經常將事情<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">定性</span>就知<span style=\"color: red;\">形象工程</span>好重要!<br />\n<br />\n文宣組加油!"}]}